snippet.title: Get Packed - Official Announcement Trailer | Stadia Connect
snippet.description:
Packing up your stuff has never been this difficult...and fun! Prepare for the ultimate co-op game with ridiculous physics and up to four player carnage. 

Get Packed dispatches to Stadia in 2020.

Pre-order Stadia Founder's Edition now at stadia.com

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: http://youtube.com/GoogleStadia
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/GoogleStadia
Follow us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/GoogleStadia
